    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Tails of Trainspot》是一款轻松的逻辑解谜游戏，背景设定在宁静的帕坎群岛。铺设铁轨连接带编号的车站，发掘岛屿的秘密，并结识迷人的动物居民。节奏舒缓，画风温馨，还有令人愉快的小游戏，带你进入一个充满奇趣与幻想的世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/16a0ad35c5a15f506dc46d364c7c4b48.poster.avif?t=1752163306\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/16a0ad35c5a15f506dc46d364c7c4b48.webm?t=1752163306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/16a0ad35c5a15f506dc46d364c7c4b48.mp4?t=1752163306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>逻辑解谜玩法</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解决基于网格的谜题，每个车站的数字表示需要连接的轨道数量。精心规划你的路线——轨道不能交叉或重叠，每个车站都必须连接到同一个网络。易学易上手，精通后成就满满。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/2e6d03c7279ff3a2b2975af6f07a21af.poster.avif?t=1752163306\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/2e6d03c7279ff3a2b2975af6f07a21af.webm?t=1752163306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/2e6d03c7279ff3a2b2975af6f07a21af.mp4?t=1752163306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>充满故事的世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索岛屿时，你会遇到各种好奇的动物居民，揭开埋藏在废墟中的神秘传说。帕坎群岛不仅仅是一个谜题板，更是一个充满个性和魅力的生动世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/20ef21626de7f78759b986aad78295b5.poster.avif?t=1752163306\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/20ef21626de7f78759b986aad78295b5.webm?t=1752163306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/20ef21626de7f78759b986aad78295b5.mp4?t=1752163306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>丰富的小游戏</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从建铁轨中暂时抽身，享受温馨的支线活动。拼装便当盒、经营饮品吧、或和当地人玩香肠骰子。这些小游戏为你的岛屿旅程增添了温暖与多样性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/ed47cca61d84b52c8de1863c7976d97a.poster.avif?t=1752163306\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/ed47cca61d84b52c8de1863c7976d97a.webm?t=1752163306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/ed47cca61d84b52c8de1863c7976d97a.mp4?t=1752163306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>轻松却富有挑战</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Tails of Trainspot》采用柔和的蒸汽时代美学与舒缓音效设计，旨在带来宁静的同时也提供令人满足的挑战。非常适合想要放松又不失深度的解谜爱好者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>让铁轨引领你踏上故事、茶香与平静之旅。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
